---
title: Spicy Thai Salmon Curry with carrot and pepper
description: Salmon is a staple in modern Thai cooking , with the country being the biggest consumer of the fish in Southeast Asia. It's unsurprising then, that Thai curry paste is such a fantastic flavour combination for this omega-rich ingredient!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R16_W25_IE_IEXCF0070-3_Main_high-1c7a163a.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.ie/recipecards/card/6602dc93aa3c1e8a85747346-en-IE.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.ie/recipes/spicy-thai-salmon-curry-6602dc93aa3c1e8a85747346
